@edoardocomar : Thanks for the patch. Perhaps we can change both the external doc and server.properties file to the following?

num.io.threads: The number of threads that the server uses for processing requests, which may introduce disk I/O.

num.network.threads: The number of threads that the server uses for receiving requests from network and sending responses to network.

